{"tid":1645740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 尋人 ］ city 人 / 職員請入","createTime":"2019-10-11T03:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:15:07.000Z","uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3fd1c28ef1a38d587da8a9b5555ab2f1409530","tid":1645740,"uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"代朋友開post ， 想尋人<br />\n事發經過如下：<br />\n<br />\n10月2號我九龍塘整電話，下午在近apple 上城大方向自動電睇，我執到張學生證，只記得係女仔，背後有一個男仔同我一齊睇，佢話佢係城大學生，可以交俾佢，佢再交俾學校。<br />\n<br />\n我想要找返當時個男仔，或有無職員，2/10當日有沒有人交過學生証去辦事處？<br />\n<br />\n我係要想知唔見學生証既學生，攞返張証未，如果未，有無職員試過聯絡遺失學生証的同學？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n更新：有城大朋友岩先去左保安室，但對方表示無學生証上既名，對方咩都唔可以提供😔 所以想盡快搵到報失嗰個男仔🙏🏻 / 事主<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n無名無相時間唔清晰，我知每日都可能會有同學唔見學生證，不過我朋友都係睇到近日的新聞而擔心，所以麻煩各位睇下有無線索"},{"pid":"31ff50a4c4d0b823f96570fb3a7db4456ebb2f54","tid":1645740,"uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:59:20.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"9852ccc3e9578bfed99fe2195bbff5fb9951ac74","tid":1645740,"uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"34fe3d400ac21ed6967817e89875ba8804192bd7","tid":1645740,"uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"df43de21e70c21686db996973dd6d268c2b752c4","tid":1645740,"uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"ce83fc0da6fbbf3b144459f33f9d425f4e1dcca8","tid":1645740,"uid":88375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"